lead_paragraph: Lewis Hamilton celebrated his first win of the Formula One season at the Monaco Grand Prix on Sunday after Mercedes told team mate Nico Rosberg to move aside and Red Bull wrecked Daniel Ricciardo's chances.

headline.print_headline: Hamilton Ends Long Wait With Monaco Win
headline.main: Hamilton Ends Long Wait With Monaco Win
